"""
Fertilizer Recommendation System - Streamlit UI
================================================
A modern, clean Streamlit dashboard for soil analysis and fertilizer recommendations.

Features:
- Two-column responsive layout
- Card-based design with custom styling
- Input validation and helper text
- Real-time recommendations display
- Professional, minimal aesthetic

Author: UI Developer
Date: 2026
"""

